WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.170 align:middle line:10%
>> A shift in the moon's orbit
may lead to massive flooding

00:00:04.170 --> 00:00:05.280 align:middle line:10%
in the future.

00:00:05.280 --> 00:00:09.660 align:middle line:84%
What's really going on with
the moon's upcoming wobble?

00:00:09.660 --> 00:00:13.029 align:middle line:90%
